trans-unit.source: The ODataLib dependencies in the Storage Client Library for .NET are resolved through the ODataLib (version 5.0.2 and greater) packages available through NuGet, and not through WCF Data Services.
trans-unit.target: The ODataLib dependencies in the Storage Client Library for .NET are resolved through the ODataLib (version 5.0.2 and greater) packages available through NuGet, and not through WCF Data Services.

trans-unit.source: The ODataLib libraries can be downloaded directly or referenced by your code project through NuGet.
trans-unit.target: The ODataLib libraries can be downloaded directly or referenced by your code project through NuGet.

trans-unit.source: The specific ODataLib packages used by the Storage Client Library are <linkText>OData</linkText><title></title>, <linkText>Edm</linkText><title></title>, and <linkText>Spatial</linkText><title></title>.
trans-unit.target: The specific ODataLib packages used by the Storage Client Library are <linkText>OData</linkText><title></title>, <linkText>Edm</linkText><title></title>, and <linkText>Spatial</linkText><title></title>.

trans-unit.source: While these libraries are used by the Azure Table storage classes, they are required dependencies for programming with the Storage Client Library.
trans-unit.target: While these libraries are used by the Azure Table storage classes, they are required dependencies for programming with the Storage Client Library.
